  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will determine pain and opioid outcomes 3 &amp; 6 months after an emergency department
      visit for acute pain. This is an observational study. Patients are enrolled during an ED
      visit and followed by telephone 3 &amp; 6 months later. Opioid databases will also be reviewed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
